    <section class="phase-section">
        <h2>Defects Found & Fixes</h2>

        <div class="cards-container">
            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>Dropdown Menu Issue</h3>
                <p>
                    The project phases menu disappeared before the user could select
                    a phase. The issue was fixed by adjusting the submenu position
                    and improving the hover behavior in CSS.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>UI/UX Page Not Found</h3>
                <p>
                    The UI/UX page did not open because the View name did not match
                    the Controller action. The issue was fixed by renaming the View
                    to UIUX.cshtml to match the MVC routing structure.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

